​​​​​​​​​​WE ARE 
   HIGHLY RESPONSIVE TO THE WORLD'S ENVIRONMENTAL AND SOCIAL 
   MEGATRENDS, TRANSLATING THEM INTO CORE 
   STRATEGIES​ THAT FEED AND DRIVE OUR 
   COMMITMENT AND 
   PERFORMANCE. THIS APPROACH GIVES US THE STIMULUS AND STRATEGIC THRUST TO FURTHER INTEGRATE 
   SUSTAINABILITY PRINCIPLES INTO OUR DAILY ACTIVITIES, CREATING 
   LONG-TERM VALUE. ​Sergio MarchionneChair​man​​
